# Floors picked so the fully-pinned closure (generated via
# ``pip-compile --generate-hashes``) limits OSV-scanner's match set
# to the exact resolved versions:
# - apache-airflow stays on the 2.x line. Airflow 3.x introduces
#   breaking changes to the test runtime (the SDK task-runner reads
#   connections from the metadata DB instead of ``AIRFLOW_CONN_*``
#   env vars; the conftest's ``dag.test()`` driver path needs a
#   significant rework to match). The unpatched-in-2.x airflow CVEs
#   are documented in ``osv-scanner.toml``.
# - apache-airflow-providers-google 11.x pairs with airflow 2.x.
# - pytest 9.0.3 closes GHSA-6w46-j5rx-g56g.
apache-airflow>=2.11.1,<3.0
apache-airflow-providers-google>=11.0,<12.0
